title: MBMBaM 269: Face 2 Face: Loose Gravy
description: In our first-ever international performance, we give the fine denizens of Vancouver our very best. We also detail the many, many ways that we've screwed up the baseline level stuff you need to know to be in Canada, because we are idiot children.
author: shows@mbmbam.com (Justin McElroy)
